  * Fixed texture object reference counting bug (bug 21756)
  * Allow depth/stencil textures to be attached to GL_STENCIL_ATTACHMENT point
    (SF bug 2793846)
  * Added missing glGet case for GL_VERTEX_ARRAY_BINDING_APPLE
