- update to Mesa bugfix release 7.0.3 RC2
  * Fixed GLX indirect vertex array rendering bug (14197)
  * Fixed crash when deleting framebuffer objects (bugs 13507,
    14293)
  * User-defined clip planes enabled for R300 (bug 9871)
